 \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Izzi_Telecom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Izzi_Telecom\"}, {\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Williams\", \"score\": 0.9999997182365348, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mariah Williams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Williams\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"High Jump\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"Rugby\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"Rugby\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"(Weightlifting\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"Sailing\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"(Athletics\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"Hockey\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"show\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The new uniforms were manufactured by ASICS and each feature green and gold colour schemes as well as an Indigenous print, making it the largest integration of Indigenous prints on athletes' uniforms in the history of the summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ASICS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asics\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"score\": 0.999863176894384, \"rank\": 0.0001368414970508886, \"text\": \"Indigenous\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"score\": 0.999863176894384, \"rank\": 0.0001368414970508886, \"text\": \"Indigenous\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The new uniforms\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"each feature green and gold colour schemes\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' uniforms\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer Olympics\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports minister Anika Wells heaped praise on those involved with the design and for reaching this achievement, while speaking at the kit launch on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anika_Wells\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anika Wells\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anika_Wells\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anika_Wells\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"praise\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"this achievement\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"the kit launch\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you to our Indigenous artist and Olympic boxer Paul Fleming and to Torres Strait artist David Bosun for your designs and for sharing 60,000 years of your culture,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"score\": 0.999863176894384, \"rank\": 0.0001368414970508886, \"text\": \"Indigenous\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Fleming_(poet)\", \"score\": 0.9499920684899182, \"rank\": 0.024291497975707083, \"text\": \"Paul Fleming\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Fleming_(poet)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Fleming_(poet)\"}, {\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boatswain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.484355872549965e-22, \"text\": \"Bosun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boatswain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boatswain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your designs\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"60,000 years\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"your culture\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Days like this are important because it is the fanfare that our Olympians deserve.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Days\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the fanfare\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"our Olympians\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many of our greatest Olympians have to work part time while competing against the world's best, where every four years their ability is decided by an inch or a millisecond - and it's their fortitude that I want to pay credit to this morning.\\\"\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our greatest Olympians\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"their ability\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"an inch\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"a millisecond\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"their fortitude\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"credit\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"this morning\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each item of uniform has been specifically tailored to suit the motion of each sport with about 460 to 480 athletes set to make up the Australian team.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1928, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9735677382755787, \"rank\": 0.021610460958316476, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each item\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"uniform\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"the motion\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"each sport\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"about 460 to 480 athletes\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chef de Mission of the Australian Olympic Team for the upcoming games and former gold medallist Olympian Anna Meares said she \\\"cannot wait\\\" to witness more iconic moments in Australian sporting history occur in the new uniforms.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1969, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999924967, \"rank\": 7.520982978256482e-12, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian sporting history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_in_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the upcoming games\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"more iconic moments\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"the new uniforms\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So many iconic Australian sporting moments played out in ASICS kit at the Tokyo Olympics, and I cannot wait to see the new sporting history Australian athletes will create in Paris in these uniforms,\\\" she said in a statement.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2234, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ASICS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asics\"}, {\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999999537510455, \"rank\": 4.289944708469667e-07, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995293365, \"rank\": 4.706581693789478e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the new sporting history\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"these uniforms\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are proud to work with ASICS and the artists to feature Aboriginal and Torres Strait artwork throughout the uniform, bringing the stories of these designs to a global audience of billions.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": 